* Thu May 04 2016 - version 0.15.0
- Remove SSL, use only TLS
- Remove QCA as a dependency
- About dialog shows which git commit was used for build
- Rename Pool/Nodes to Devices

* Mon Jan 19 2015 - version 0.14.0
- Automatic clibboard tracking is optional
- CLI, command haveclip sync

* Sat Aug 02 2014 - version 0.13.0
- Removed paste services
- Removed serial mode
- Removed unification of clipboard and selection
- Settings:
  - Connection split to Network and Security
  - Certificate generation
  - New node pairing wizard
  - Customizable nodes
  - Node auto-discovery
  - Clipboard size limits
  - MIME filtering
  - Reset
- On-demand clipboard sync
- New graphics
